{"tid":876634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"得州男「暗網」徵少女遺體性交吃屍　密探放假餌擒變態男 (23:34)","createTime":"2018-10-25T17:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T01:58:14.000Z","uid":145589,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f045470f506b446029e468363a114febfe7abfcc","tid":876634,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/014138_2ee5dcc08a9e685dec0f6c558292a39f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F014138_2ee5dcc08a9e685dec0f6c558292a39f.png&h=ca85aeb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國得州一名男子於暗網（deep web）徵求一具年輕女子遺體，企圖用作性交或食下屍體。當地警方發現後派卧底密探於網上與男子接觸，男子透過電郵進一步向探員透露詳細方案。兩人及後相約「交收」時，男子當場被捕。<br />\n<br />\n探員假扮成一名父親，向男子稱願意將他的女兒作交易。涉案21歲男子巴特爾（Alexander Nathan Bater）信以為真，在電郵詢問可否真的殺死你的女兒，又指「我不會改變想法，真的想去實行。」巴特爾之後又叫探員準備新手機及新衣服，準備殺人後處理工作。<br />\n<br />\n雙方相約在一間酒店「交收」，巴特爾當場被警方拘捕，警員在他身上找到一把刀。目前巴特爾被控誘騙，謀殺未遂，串謀謀殺，以及企圖對兒童發生性行為。地區檢察官表示，暗網的資訊對孩子的安全構成威脅，並且日益嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n（鏡報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181024/s00005/1540392982423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181024%2Fs00005%2F1540392982423&d=3yIpaL2E6bo%2F5HUhI5S2uNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=34f284b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181024%2Fs00005%2F1540392982423&h=0eb26868\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181024/s00005/1540392982423</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85957c1b22d549030fecba37c4db94e9df2aa994","tid":876634,"uid":167330,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:48:34.000Z","msg":"暗網一早俾人啤實晒，仲夠膽喺到搞呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bfd1bb49b78b2da2ad14cdcbf257fc0e46ce9d6","tid":876634,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980a7ac1332e8ce29433dce21be239ed51fb8f42","tid":876634,"uid":82917,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:52:20.000Z","msg":"睇標題都想嘔"},{"pid":"64e34ee7b7b7dc6c06b4827d48e0449d4d8008c1","tid":876634,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:53:47.000Z","msg":"唔知會坐幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee95f3e256eae9cd866b19cea8c5ff9b3e1c0da","tid":876634,"uid":61989,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46b6c56d29473e000ef805b7dbba82b523f3ddc9","tid":876634,"uid":45368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:56:43.000Z","msg":"右邊張相仲靚仔過唔少連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82c2c4e90992d648b4b3799f8a5d60b02d7deb5","tid":876634,"uid":40940,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"同劉馬車發顛個樣好似"},{"pid":"8d1975ea49c96cc9b5c02c11e45feadc4c49c3d1","tid":876634,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ee95f3e256eae9cd866b19cea8c5ff9b3e1c0da","tid":876634,"uid":61989,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T18:01:29.000Z","msg":"樣子反映一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a8864f46e98775c7486a3a0a8ae0f54bb734b8","tid":876634,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"<im